{"lastModified":1768043906843,"uri":"c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands\n\nOKEANA is a 14.94m / 49ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2020 by Bali Catamarans. Sleeping 8 guests in 4 cabins and with a crew of 2. The guest cabins comprise of four a queen cabins and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"OKEANA","images":["/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::74wUE5w-L.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-i6fQH2a_3.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-X24bEG6rmA.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-s0ydN7Vlv.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-3C5oLp8nQ.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-0nTNZpOb7.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-P2NSap3GB.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-PT_7ZSXF1R.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-_78LNqcoTh.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-i-fQgCq3r.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-qkJt-EViD.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-n9ZmXM4XF.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-37q3oPhKB.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-Fr2FKObXO.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-dm27MJt5O.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100315-98Kwq3Khx.jpg/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Bali Catamarans","model":"","maxCrew":2,"sleeps":8,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::a0201b56-b3ee-11ed-8a74-325096b39f47","name":"Tortola","coordinates":{"latitude":18.4335216,"longitude":-64.63325746},"country":"British Virgin Islands"},"builtYear":2020,"interiorDesigner":"","cruiseSpeed":0,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Queen Cabins","value":"4"}],"cabins":4,"bathrooms":4,"length":14.94,"beam":7.88,"draft":1.31,"hullType":"Catamaran","superStructure":[],"engines":"2 x 57hp","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Hairdryers"},{"label":"BBQ"},{"label":"Gym/Exercise"},{"label":"Sailing Instructions"},{"label":"Deck shower"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Hammock"},{"label":"Sun Awning"},{"label":"Special Diets"},{"label":"Yoga Mats"},{"label":"Ice Maker"}],"toys":[{"label":"Snorkel Gear"},{"label":"Tube"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"Kayaks (2 Pax)"},{"label":"Floating Dock (10 pax)"},{"label":"Swim Platform"},{"label":"Boarding Ladder"},{"label":"Beach Games"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"},{"label":"Deep Sea Fish"},{"label":"Underwater Camera"},{"label":"Underwater Video"},{"label":"Sea Scooter","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Noodles"}],"entertainment":["Salon TV","Salon Stereo","Onboard Wi-Fi","iPod/Device Hookups"],"tenders":["13ft Highfield Center Console with 40 HP engine (10 pax)"]},"crew":[{"name":"Dal Flynn","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::a380fea0-9f89-11ee-ad9a-934470971fdd.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Captain Dal comes from Yorkshire, in the North of England, and has been sailing since childhood, serving as a professional Captain for 11 years through the Mediterranean, Caribbean and Bahamas. Specialising almost exclusively in crewed yachts and luxury crewed charters, onboard sailing catamarans, and monohulls upto 76 feet, Dal's love for sailing and the yachting lifestyle as a whole has extended into a passion for new adventures, immersing himself in a variety of cultures, meeting new and unlikely people, and hospitality.\n\nEnsuring that he and his team provide their clients the absolute best possible experience on and offboard is a top priority, whilst providing a guest-focused, engaging, friendly and fun atmosphere. Dal is a keen and enthusiastic free diver, scuba diver, sailor, engineer, motorsports and soccer lover, and exceptionally laid-back and easygoing."},{"name":"Anna Vann","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc2520-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ff3c6f40-ee15-11f0-8a04-7f2c03578fa2/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Chef Anna is a private yacht chef and experienced sailor who has completed a full circumnavigation, blending global flavours with the effortless luxury of life at sea.\nHer cuisine brings together vibrant Asian influences with the light, elegant spirit of the French Riviera — perfect for long, sunlit days onboard. Guests can expect fresh, Asian-inspired lunches full of colour and energy, followed by relaxed, refined three-course dinners crafted in a modern French style.\n\nFor Anna, cooking is both joy and meditation. She loves creating clean, flavour-forward dishes, including vegan and keto-friendly desserts that feel indulgent yet nourishing.\n\nAs a yoga teacher, she brings balance, mindfulness, and a sense of wellbeing into her galley. Every plate is prepared with care, intention, and a genuine desire to make guests feel pampered, satisfied, and at home on the water."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":2000000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":2000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":2400000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":2400000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Summer/Winter - Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-12-14T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"USD","charterFee":2000000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2000000,"amount":2000000,"conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded"}],"total":2000000,"subTotal":2000000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"U.S. Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","U.S. Virgin Is."],"coordinates":[-64.79221690684143,18.050874527948764],"bbox":[-65.0236328125,17.701708984375003,-64.58046875,18.385205078124997]},{"label":"British Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","British Virgin Is."],"coordinates":[-64.45080373172777,18.568736231458896],"bbox":[-64.69511718749999,18.399121093749997,-64.273583984375,18.752685546875]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"Summer/Winter - High Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-12-15T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-04-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-12-15T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-04-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-12-15T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-04-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"USD","charterFee":2400000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2400000,"amount":2400000,"conditions":"VAT & APA Excluded"}